Remove a Running Container:
docker container rm -f <container_id_or_name> bash

  Remove a Stopped Container:
docker container rm <container_id_or_name>  bash

  Remove All Containers:
docker container rm $(docker ps -a -q)

  Remove Multiple Containers:
docker container rm <container_id_or_name1> <container_id_or_name2> ...

Remove a Directory and its Contents using rm:

rm -r /path/to/directory

  syntax : remove directoryname
rm -rf  <directoryname>

  
